Zimbabwe’s Power Shortages Likely to Persist Until 2013, Daily News Says

-- B y   G o d f r e y   M a r a w a n y i k a
-- 
2011-09-02T07:43:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/zimbabwe-s-power-shortages-likely-to-persist-until-2013-daily-news-says.html
Zimbabwe ’s power shortages will
probably persist until 2013 when an agreement to sell
electricity to  Namibia  ends, the Daily News reported, citing
Energy Minister Elton Mangoma.  Zimbabwe exports 150 megawatts of power to Namibia, the
Harare-based newspaper cited Mangoma as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
